I. About
========

The qt-gui directory contains the primesieve GUI application developed
with the Qt framework (http://qt-project.org).

II. Qt project file (MSVC, GNU g++, Intel icpc)
===============================================

* primesieve.pro
  primesieve project file for the Qt-Creator IDE (e.g. to edit the
  source code or build a primesieve executable).

III. Source files
=================

* src/PrimeSieveGUI.cpp & .h
  Contains the graphical user interface code.
* src/PrimeSieveGUI_menu.cpp
  Contains code related to the menu bar.
* src/PrimeSieveProcess.cpp & .h
  Class that is used for prime sieving. PrimeSieveProcess launches
  a ParallelPrimeSieve instance in a separate process, this approach
  allows to easily cancel sieving by killing the process.
  The communication between the GUI process (PrimeSieveGUI) and the
  ParallelPrimeSieve instance is realised via shared memory.
* src/main.cpp
  Contains the ParallelPrimeSieve code launched by PrimeSieveProcess
  objects.
